00:09:25.764 --> 00:09:28.784
Okay. Well, we'll start with Gabrielle.

162
00:09:28.844 --> 00:09:32.704
I remember when I started to get the phone calls and the emails, I think 28, 29

163
00:09:32.804 --> 00:09:33.224
January,

164
00:09:34.584 --> 00:09:35.024
2020,

165
00:09:35.964 --> 00:09:36.044
it-

166
00:09:36.304 --> 00:09:36.724
COVID.

167
00:09:37.124 --> 00:09:38.824
For COVID. So very... What did I say?

168
00:09:39.604 --> 00:09:39.614
Gabrielle.

169
00:09:39.624 --> 00:09:39.634
Gabrielle.

170
00:09:39.644 --> 00:09:40.554
Sorry. COVID.

171
00:09:40.584 --> 00:09:42.144
I was thinking that doesn't sound like Gabrielle.

172
00:09:42.244 --> 00:09:43.464
Yeah. That's right. Sorry.

173
00:09:44.644 --> 00:09:45.344
So it became

174
00:09:46.224 --> 00:09:49.864
very clear quickly that Chinese market was gonna

175
00:09:49.904 --> 00:09:50.923
close, and it did.

176
00:09:52.004 --> 00:09:55.744
So that's at a fairly important point of the fishing year for rock lobster

177
00:09:55.824 --> 00:09:59.524
because Chinese New Year normally occurs end of January, beginning of February.

178
00:09:59.604 --> 00:10:01.084
So there was a lot of uncaught ACE.

179
00:10:02.124 --> 00:10:05.664
Now, in this case, the government reacted fairly quickly

