forward to decline it on the basis there are sustainability issues.

230
00:12:53.304 --> 00:12:53.504
Mm-hmm.

231
00:12:53.884 --> 00:12:54.254
Susan.

232
00:12:54.344 --> 00:12:56.824
No, my questions have been answered. So it was about the carry forward.

233
00:12:56.864 --> 00:12:57.013
Thank you very much.

234
00:12:57.064 --> 00:12:58.024
Okay. Steve.

235
00:12:58.384 --> 00:12:59.524
Yeah, mine's in a similar

