00:13:22.604 --> 00:13:26.464
you have a control on total removals from the fishery-

243
00:13:26.784 --> 00:13:26.854
Yep

244
00:13:26.984 --> 00:13:30.784
... that maintains the stock at its management targets and avoids breaching

